FOLLOWING  
WATCHED Series (2023)  
Digital (JPEG, via Adobe Illustrator & Photoshop only)  
3240px x 5760px

-

About the WATCHED Series:

WATCHED is an autobiographic series inspired by my collective experiences of being stalked. This collection explores my retrospection and thoughts through a very familiar material —googly eyes. It moves in many directions. It can move to make you feel watched.
